text:
Hi, happy holidays.

I recently launched Analytics for Cloudflare, a native app for iPhone, iPad & Mac to show Cloudflare Analytics data wherever you go.

I am looking forward to some feedback on the app as well as any features you would like to see in the future.

Enjoy, — Alex
